Company Overview of North Lion Holding Corp.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
North Lion Holding Corp., a management holding company, provides assistance to businesses in various industries. The company also offers consulting services for start-up, growing plans, management, and marketing. In addition, it provides services in the areas of branding experience, factory and contract, IT projects, business consultation, fast growing business, and supporting and financing. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Lewes, Delaware.


16192 Coastal HighwayLewes, DE 19958United StatesFounded in 2014



