Capitol Chilled Foods[edit]
Lion also has a controlling interest in Capitol Chilled Foods (Australia) Pty Ltd, which is the Australian Capital Territory's sole dairy manufacturer. Bega Cheese Ltd owns a 25% stake. The company has the following brands:[48]

Canberra Milk
Canberra Gold

